  "contents": "<div class=\"content markitup-box\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t国人对柴静采访丁仲礼这段视频的反应，也是颇为经典。他们不了解是非曲直，只根据洗脑所得和个人立场，大骂柴静、追捧丁仲礼。<br/>\n<br/>\r\n然而，2020年习近平已提出要实现“碳中和”，等于在事实和立场上都否定了丁仲礼的观点。但国人仍然继续大骂柴静、追捧丁仲礼，另一方面又支持习近平的碳中和。他们似乎看不出来二者是矛盾的、自身立场是分裂的。这就是完全的愚民和暴民<br/>\n<br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvNjBlNGFmNGY4MjhkYjQxMDcyNTU0LnBuZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/60e4af4f828db41072554.png\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/60e4af4f828db41072554.png\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/60e4af4f828db41072554.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvYjkxYTQzNzMyMjYzYWQxZWI1ZmQ1LnBuZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/b91a43732263ad1eb5fd5.png\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/b91a43732263ad1eb5fd5.png\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/b91a43732263ad1eb5fd5.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvN2U5NzEyZTExNjkyNDU5YTlhZWY5LnBuZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/7e9712e11692459a9aef9.png\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/7e9712e11692459a9aef9.png\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/7e9712e11692459a9aef9.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvYzEwZWRhNGJkNTY4NDgwMmVhZWZlLnBuZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/c10eda4bd5684802eaefe.png\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/c10eda4bd5684802eaefe.png\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/c10eda4bd5684802eaefe.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvNGRmMDIwMTRjYTk1ZTRhYzY2Nzg4LnBuZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/4df02014ca95e4ac66788.png\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/4df02014ca95e4ac66788.png\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/4df02014ca95e4ac66788.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvZGUxZjAzZGZlOTdkZTNlNTJlZjdhLnBuZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/de1f03dfe97de3e52ef7a.png\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/de1f03dfe97de3e52ef7a.png\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/de1f03dfe97de3e52ef7a.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvMTAzNTg2NGY1Y2Y0Y2VjMGNhNmYwLnBuZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/1035864f5cf4cec0ca6f0.png\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/1035864f5cf4cec0ca6f0.png\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/1035864f5cf4cec0ca6f0.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\n<br/>\n<br/>\r\n对了，那些还对气候问题持怀疑甚至否定态度的，看看这几年河南洪灾、四川干旱、江南热射病。以后只会越来越多<br/>\n<br/>\r\n“好日子”还长着呢<br/>\n<br/>\r\n关于气候变化问题，我写过一篇文章，在品葱也发过：<br/>\n<br/>\n<a href=\"https://pincong.rocks/article/44292\" title=\"https://pincong.rocks/article/44292\">气候变化下的中国与国人</a> </div>",
